<p>Tel-el-Kebir</p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>
<p>Just arrived here from the Peninsula. I received the "Sentimental Bloke" at Lemnos on my way over. It was like bumping into an old cobber from home.</p>
<p>I lent it round and the fellows reckoned it was good.</p>
<p>I guess people at home, had a shock when they heard of the evacuation It was pretty hard leaving after all that had been done, I can't say we were particularly anxious to stay there.</p>
<p>I was there just over four month</p>
